    /**
     * Extract structured JSON from a document using JSON-encoded preset spec and options.
     *
     * This is the synchronous JSON-in / JSON-out entry point suitable for FFI and
     * language-binding call paths.
     * {@literal @}param bytes — raw document bytes.
     *
     * {@literal @}param mime — MIME type string.
     *
     * {@literal @}param presetSpecJsonJsonString {@code {"named":"id"}} or {@code {"inline":{...}}}.
     *
     * {@literal @}param optionsJson — JSON string mirroring StructuredOptions fields (except {@code cache}).  Pass {@code "{}"} to use
     * all defaults.
     *
     * {@literal @}return JSON-serialised {@code StructuredOutput} on success.
     *
     * {@literal @}throws XbergRsException Returns {@code Validation} when either JSON argument is
     * malformed.  All other failures from the underlying
     * {@code extract_structured_sync} call are mapped onto {@code XbergError}
     * via From&lt;StructuredError&gt;(super.StructuredError).
     */
